 "elapsed_ms": 73.56, "extra": {"entity_stack_count": 5, "conversation_history_count": 2, "previous_result_skus_count": 0, "recommendation_context_present": false}}, {"stage": "named_product_shortcut", "elapsed_ms": 2.16, "extra": {"hit": false, "agent_mode": null}}, {"stage": "plan_conversation_route.llm", "elapsed_ms": 4972.54, "extra": {"llm_called": true, "query_type": "scene_description", "resolved_skus": []}}, {"stage": "plan_conversation_route", "elapsed_ms": 4972.98, "extra": {"llm_called": true, "query_type": "scene_description", "resolved_skus": []}}, {"stage": "route_deterministic_fact_question", "elapsed_ms": 0.17, "extra": {"hit": false, "intent": null, "agent_mode": null}}, {"stage": "hybrid_search_products.semantic_retrieve", "elapsed_ms": 344.14, "extra": {"semantic_query": "露营多人做饭", "semantic_rows": 20}}, {"stage": "hybrid_search_products.breakdown", "elapsed_ms": 80.02, "extra": {"sql_filter_ms": 5.46, "embedding_query_ms": 0.0, "vector_search_ms": 0.0, "merge_rank_ms": 0.01, "get_detail_ms": 80.0, "candidates_count": 0, "prompt_chars": 0}}, {"stage": "tool.execute_async", "elapsed_ms": 427.16, "extra": {"tool": "hybrid_search_products", "async_call": true, "ok": true}}, {"stage": "process_agent_request", "elapsed_ms": 10720.45, "extra": {"hit": true, "intent": "compare_products", "agent_mode": "llm_tool_calling"}}, {"stage": "hybrid_search_products.semantic_retrieve", "elapsed_ms": 351.76, "extra": {"semantic_query": "LOADTEST_RUN_ID=20260621_005444_warmup 推荐三款适合露营多人做饭的套锅，并说明区别", "semantic_rows": 50}}, {"stage": "hybrid_search_products.breakdown", "elapsed_ms": 128.28, "extra": {"sql_filter_ms": 45.51, "embedding_query_ms": 0.0, "vector_search_ms": 0.0, "merge_rank_ms": 0.01, "get_detail_ms": 128.03, "candidates_count": 10, "prompt_chars": 23429}}, {"stage": "tool.execute_async", "elapsed_ms": 481.79, "extra": {"tool": "hybrid_search_products", "async_call": true, "ok": true}}, {"stage": "process_intent_request_retry", "elapsed_ms": 38808.35, "extra": {"hit": true, "intent": "recommend_products"}}, {"stage": "save_messages_and_commit", "elapsed_ms": 24.63, "extra": {"branch": "agent", "skip_polish": true}}, {"stage": "ask_customer_service.total", "elapsed_ms": 49632.99, "extra": {"branch": "agent", "intent": "recommend_products", "agent_mode": null}}], "first_answer_delta_ms": 10348.54, "done_ms": null, "final_answer": "针对你“露营多人做饭”的需求，这里有两款非常合适的套锅，以及一个同样适合多人场景的炒锅单品可选，它们的详细区别如下：\n\n首选推荐：炊墨套锅（CW-C83）\n包含一个3700ML汤锅和一个2300ML煎盘，总重2000g，锅体为硬质氧化铝合金搭配白蜡木手柄，采用水性不沾涂层，健康无油也不粘。最大亮点是全炉具兼容（明火、燃气、卡式炉、电磁炉、电陶炉等），并配有快拆手柄，一拧就能拆卸，收纳和装拆都很方便。3.7升+2.3升的组合容量足够3-4人一锅炖煮、同时煎炒，很适合家庭精致露营或营地大餐。\n\n备选：2-4人野餐锅10件套（CW-C05-37）\n这是一套完整的10件配件套装，含1.7L锅、1.4L浅锅和7.5英寸煎盘，附带碗、勺、铲等餐具，总重仅1030g，非常轻便。锅体采用硬质氧化铝合金，耐摔耐磨，整套可收纳在一个包装中。推荐它的理由是性价比极高，一套开箱就能满足煎、炒、煮、炖全场景，专为3-4人家庭出行或小型团建设计，适合首次露营或不想额外购买配件的用户。\n\n补充单品：炊墨炒锅（CW-C83-1）\n如果煮炖需求远大于煎盘需求，这款3700ML大容量炒锅也很适合搭配使用，重1200g，材质和涂层与炊墨套锅一致，同样全炉具兼容、快拆手柄。它不是套锅，但3.7升容量在多人露营时可以作为主力煮锅或汤锅，兼顾炒菜。缺点是没有煎盘和额外配件，如需煎烤建议搭配单独煎盘。\n\n三款产品的核心区别在于：炊墨套锅兼顾煮与煎，容量最大，功能最全面且全炉具通吃；2-4人野餐锅10件套则是轻量一体化方案，配件最齐全，重量最轻，但锅体相对较小（最大1.7L），适合轻装简行；炊墨炒锅是单品，容量同样大，但缺少套锅的多样性。可根据你是不是更看重全面烹饪功能、还是更追求轻便与配件一步到位来选择。", "intent": "recommend_products", "agent_mode": null}}
