ommendation_rank_and_prepare", "elapsed_ms": 89.89, "extra": {"ranked_count": 5, "enriched_count": 5}}, {"stage": "process_agent_request", "elapsed_ms": 11514.83, "extra": {"hit": true, "intent": "recommend_products", "agent_mode": "llm_tool_calling"}}, {"stage": "save_messages_and_commit", "elapsed_ms": 21.42, "extra": {"branch": "agent", "skip_polish": true}}, {"stage": "ask_customer_service.total", "elapsed_ms": 11542.56, "extra": {"branch": "agent", "intent": "recommend_products", "agent_mode": "llm_tool_calling"}}], "first_answer_delta_ms": 9452.07, "done_ms": null, "final_answer": "综合考虑轻量便携和中等预算，推荐露营锅具套装 CW-C01-37。它定位中端，价格更符合您的预算，同时重量控制在 595g，在同类型双人套锅里属于轻量选手，并且支持燃气和酒精双燃料，适用性广。另外几款更轻的产品如 CS-B14 酒精炉（300g）、CW-C93 单锅（220g）和 CW-C97 水壶（183g）等，虽然重量更极致，但价格定位均为高端，超预算较多；CW-K02-37 虽然价格入门且仅 150g，但仅为 800ml 水壶，场景较单一。综合来看，CW-C01-37 在重量、预算和功能丰富度上取得了较好的平衡。", "intent": "recommend_products", "agent_mode": "llm_tool_calling"}}
